I got a response. I like that. I'm more than willing to<br>
contribute where I have enough knowledge or insight to<br>
contribute. Otherwise, I'll keep my mouth shut.<br><br>
Doc Del, I don't know you and very little about you. On<br>
the other hand maybe I do. I know that anger when I see<br>
it.<br><br>
I don't need you to get a clue. As a matter of fact this<br>
site might be one small thing you need. You aren't unique.<br>
On the other hand, you're reaction to my statements, even<br>
when I explained I was unfamiliar with what this site was<br>
about, is. We all have anger. You are on the edge pal.<br><br>
You aren't alone with dreams. You aren't alone with having<br>
searched a long time in a lot of places for some peace. If<br>
you find it here, great. But it obviously hasn't been enuf<br>
yet. I ain't your enemy. To strike out against my innocent<br>
posting should be an indicator to you. If you want to talk<br>
to me about, fine. If you want to tell me to go to Hell, <br>
fine. This is the internet, and hell, anyone can say what<br>
they want.<br><br>
My anger comes and goes. My memories now come and go. In<br>
my heart of hearts, it is never but a heartbeat away. Nam<br>
lives in me and those like us. But part of healing is to<br>
change. Do you want to continue this dialog, or do you<br>
just want to tell me to go to Hell. It's up to you. We are<br>
brothers after all. I got ahead on some of my shit, but I<br>
will hurt to my grave. The one I walked away from there.<br><br>
To Arthur Varonelli, sorry if my posting seemed to demean.<br>
I only got to read the postings at the site the evening I<br>
dropped by. I intend to drop by here again and learn. I can<br>
confess to a bitterness to the protesters. Yet, they were<br>
my own people, generation. It's one I still struggle to<br>
keep perspective on. Let me assure all who have read what<br>
I have written, I am both quick and slow to judge. But I<br>
am not a fool. I will be back to see what this is all about.<br>
Not that any of you give a shit. Not necessary. I understand<br>
that I am still a stranger here. Don't mean nothin.<br><br>
Hope you and Doc Del give me some more input so I can<br>
tell if I can come here and get some of the stuff I know<br>
I need, but still cannot define.<br><br>
See ya back in the World.<br>

